changes to the sql queriy SQL_GETALL_STREAMPOSTS_AND_USERBASIC
affects the following class:
 StreamListViewFactory 
   the value retrieval from cursor must use the correct column index
 StreamActivity
   setGroupIdCursorColumnIndex must be supplied with the right index pointing to the post_id in the result query.
 ApplicationDBHelper.START_STREAM_INDEX_GETALL_STREAMPOSTS_AND_USERBASIC
   the value must point to the start index of the stream result columns. 
 
